ent iterations**: Validates return of `None` when max iterations reached\\n\\n### 4. Maximization Tests (2 test cases)\\n- **maximize negative quadratic**: Finds maximum of `-(x-2)Â² + 5`\\n- **maximizeWith**: Tests custom parameters for maximization\\n\\n### 5. Error Handling Tests (6 test cases)\\n- **NaN lower bound**: Should throw exception\\n- **Infinity upper bound**: Should throw exception\\n- **NaN tolerance**: Should throw exception\\n- **Zero tolerance**: Should throw exception (must be positive)\\n- **Negative tolerance**: Should throw exception\\n- **Function returns NaN/Infinity**: Should throw when function is not finite\\n\\n### 6. Edge Cases (3 test cases)\\n- **Reversed bounds**: Tests automatic swapping when upper \\u003c lower\\n- **Narrow interval**: Tests convergence in small interval [-0.1, 0.1]\\n- **Absolute value function**: Tests non-smooth function\\n\\n### 7. Additional Function Types (4 test cases)\\n- **Cosine function**: Periodic function with known minima/maxima\\n- **Quartic function**: More complex polynomial\\n- Various other test functions to ensure robustness\\n\\n## Test Coverage Results\\n\\n### Brent Module (Optimization/BrentExt.fs)\\n| Metric | Before | After | Improvement |\\n|--------|--------|-------|-------------|\\n| **Line Coverage** | 0/120 (0.0%) | **120/120 (100.0%)** | **+120 lines (+100.0 pp)** |\\n| **Branch Coverage** | 0/112 (0.0%) | **108/112 (96.4%)** | **+108 branches (+96.4 pp)** |\\n\\n### Overall Project Coverage\\n| Metric | Before | After | Improvement |\\n|--------|--------|-------|-------------|\\n| **Points** | 14,371/37,939 (37.88%) | 14,552/38,060 (38.23%) | **+181 points (+0.35 pp)** |\\n| **Methods** | 3,837/10,597 (36.21%) | 3,896/10,652 (36.58%) | **+59 methods (+0.37 pp)** |\\n| **Classes** | 2,512/4,210 (59.67%) | 2,565/4,265 (60.14%) | **+53 classes (+0.47 pp)** |\\n| **Branches** | 4,569/32,246 (14.17%) | 4,668/32,341 (14.43%) | **+99 branches (+0.26 pp)** |\\n| **Total Tests** | 1,588 | **